All reusable components live in `src/components/ui/` and `src/components/layout/`.

### UI Components (`src/components/ui/`)
| Component           | File               | Library              | Key Styling Notes                                       |
|---------------------|--------------------|----------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| `Button`            | `Button.jsx`       | `class-variance-authority` + `@radix-ui/react-slot` | 6 variants: default, destructive, outline, secondary, ghost, link. 4 sizes: default, sm, lg, icon. |
| `Badge`             | `Badge.jsx`        | `class-variance-authority` | 4 variants: default, secondary, destructive, outline. No rounded corners. |
| `Card`              | `Card.jsx`         | Custom               | `border border-border bg-card shadow-none`. Sub-components: CardHeader, CardTitle, CardDescription, CardContent, CardFooter. |
| `Dialog`            | `Dialog.jsx`       | `@radix-ui/react-dialog` | Overlay: `bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm`. Content: `border border-border bg-background p-6 shadow-lg`. Close button with `<X>` icon. |
| `Table`             | `Table.jsx`        | Custom               | Row hover: `hover:bg-secondary/50`. Header text: `text-muted-foreground font-medium`. Borders: `border-b border-border`. |
