| `Badge`             | `Badge.jsx`        | CVA                  | `px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold`. No rounded corners. |
| `Separator`         | `Separator.jsx`    | Custom               | Thin horizontal rule using `border-border`.              |
| `Sheet`             | `Sheet.jsx`        | `@radix-ui/react-dialog` | Mobile navigation drawer. Side-aware for RTL.            |
| `NavigationMenu`    | `NavigationMenu.jsx`| `@radix-ui/react-navigation-menu` | Desktop dropdown menus with team listings.               |
| `SectionTitle`      | `SectionTitle.jsx` | Custom               | Left border accent: `border-l-4 border-primary pl-4`. RTL-aware: `rtl:border-l-0 rtl:border-r-4 rtl:pl-0 rtl:pr-4`. |
| `StatCounter`       | `StatCounter.jsx`  | Custom               | Animated number counters for homepage stats.              |
| `Accordion`         | `Accordion.jsx`    | Custom               | Collapsible FAQ/info sections.                            |
| `Tag`               | `Tag.jsx`          | Custom               | Small keyword/label tags.                                 |
| `LdreasLogo`        | `LdreasLogo.jsx`   | Custom SVG           | Inline SVG logo component with `variant` prop.            |

### Layout Components (`src/components/layout/`)
| Component    | File            | Purpose                                               |
|-------------|-----------------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| `Header`    | `Header.jsx`    | Top institutional identity bar (university name, etc.) |
| `NavBar`    | `NavBar.jsx`    | Sticky navigation with desktop menu + mobile Sheet     |
| `PageHero`  | `PageHero.jsx`  | Full-width banner with breadcrumb + page title `<h1>` |
| `Footer`    | `Footer.jsx`    | 3-column footer with links, contact, language switcher |

