| Role            | Key                | Dashboard Tabs                                              |
|-----------------|--------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Member**      | `member`           | Profile Editor, My Publications                             |
| **Team Leader** | `team_leader`      | Profile Editor, My Publications, Manage Projects, Team Personnel |
