## 14. Accessibility

- Every page has `<main id="main-content">`.
- Skip link: `<a href="#main-content" className="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>`.
- All interactive elements have unique `id` attributes.
- `aria-label` on icon-only buttons.
- `aria-hidden="true"` on decorative separators.
- Focus ring: `ring-2 ring-ring ring-offset-2` via `*:focus-visible` in global CSS.
- Semantic HTML: `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`, `<article>`, `<aside>`.
- Navigation has `role="navigation"` and `aria-label="Main navigation"`.
- Footer has `role="contentinfo"`.

---

## 15. Image Handling

- Project/News images use `photo_url` field (external URL string).
- Render with aspect-ratio container:
  ```jsx
  <div className="aspect-video w-full overflow-hidden border border-border bg-secondary/10">
    <img src={url} alt="..." className="h-full w-full object-cover" />
  </div>
  ```
- Fallback for missing images: grey placeholder div with a centered Lucide icon.
- **No border-radius** on image containers.

