## 18. Naming Conventions

| Item            | Convention                              | Example                    |
|-----------------|----------------------------------------|----------------------------|
| Components      | PascalCase                              | `PageHero`, `SectionTitle` |
| Files (components)| PascalCase `.jsx`                     | `Button.jsx`, `Card.jsx`  |
| Files (hooks)   | camelCase with `use` prefix             | `useTranslation.js`        |
| Files (services)| camelCase                               | `dbService.js`             |
| CSS classes     | Tailwind utilities only                 | No BEM, no CSS modules     |
| Translation keys| camelCase                               | `navHome`, `loginTitle`    |
| Route paths     | kebab-case                              | `/news/:id`, `/members/:id`|
| Database fields | snake_case                              | `full_name`, `team_id`     |

---

## 19. Do's and Don'ts — Quick Reference

### ✅ DO
- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils.js` to merge Tailwind classes
- Use `text-start` instead of `text-left` for RTL compatibility
- Use Radix primitives for overlays, dialogs, sheets, and navigation menus
- Use `font-serif` for all headings and titles
- Use `rounded-none` / `--radius: 0px` everywhere
- Use `border border-border` for all container outlines
- Use `shadow-none` or `shadow-sm` maximum
- Flash-dismiss success/error messages after 4s
- Wrap page content in `container-custom`
- Give all forms and interactive elements unique `id` attributes

### ❌ DON'T
- Use `window.confirm()`, `window.alert()`, or `window.prompt()`
- Use rounded corners (`rounded-md`, `rounded-lg`, `rounded-full`)
- Use raw hex colors — always use token classes
- Use FontAwesome, Heroicons, or emoji for icons
- Use CSS Modules, styled-components, or inline `style` props
- Use `text-left` or `text-right` — use `text-start` / `text-end`
- Use large shadows (`shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`, `shadow-xl`)
- Add new fonts without updating `global.css` custom properties
- Combine `.grid` and `.flex-row-reverse-rtl` on the same element
- Create new components outside `src/components/ui/` or `src/components/layout/`
